data.description: RARE FIND!! This single-story, semi-custom home is exceptional and excellently built with the design features that set it apart. Its main house on this quarter acre property boasts a beautiful, open, and welcoming floor plan, that seamlessly connects living, dining, and kitchen. As you enter this home, your welcomed into a grand formal living and dining room where you are greeted with soaring ceilings and natural lighting through a wall of windows. Granite countertops, an ample sized island and generous cabinet space, this gourmet kitchen is perfect for entertaining both family friendly parties and elegant soirées. The master bedroom can be your own mini penthouse get away with spa like master bathroom. Huge secondary rooms connected by jack and jill bathroom. Take a stroll out back to your parklike back yard with large casita that has its own full bathroom, kitchenette and closet. Don’t pass up this gem in the desert that could be your next home in a gorgeous guard gated community
